The paper deals with uncertainty quantification in regression problems using deep learning techniques. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with image data and face recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of mixture density networks (MDNs) is a statistical method, which falls under statistics (cs.STAT). Finally, the paper deals with time-series data, which falls under neural networks (cs.NE).
